1. Kupio sam novu *gumu* za bicikl. (I bought a new *tire* for my bike.)
2. Na putu sam promenio *gume* na autu. (I changed the *tires* on my car during the trip.)
3. Držite se za *gume* u vožnji autobusa. (Hold onto the *handles* while riding the bus.)
4. *Gumom* sam obrisao fleku na stolu. (I wiped the stain off the table with a *rubber* eraser.)
5. Ovaj materijal je *gumast*. (This material is *rubbery*.)
6. Pukla mi je *guma* na balonu. (The *balloon* popped on me.)
7. Uradite ovo kružnim pokretima sa *gumicom*. (Do this in circular motions with a *rubber band*.)
8. Gornji deo *gume* na ovom čizmi je pocepan. (The upper part of the *boot* is torn.)
9. Ovo je *gumeno* crevo za zalivanje bašte. (This is a *rubber* hose for watering the garden.)
10. Dizajnirao sam novi proizvod od *gume*. (I designed a new product made of *rubber*.)

Note: The word "guma" in Serbian can refer to both "tire" and "rubber" depending on the context, hence the different translations.